{"tid":646080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★加入貿易戰？台灣宣布中興列入出口管制對象","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T08:36:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d5060190bf4e9124550855989eb57fbe3ae663","tid":646080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"中國大陸與美國的貿易戰開打，震驚世界，連台灣亦想參一腳？台灣的經濟部周五（27日）透露，指為確保台灣高科技業界的出口權益，經濟部已將中興通訊及中興康訊兩間公司，列入「戰略性高科技貨品出口管制對象」，台商出口貨品至該兩間公司前，須事先取得許可證，再向海關報運出口，經濟部國際貿易局已於周一（23日）致函相關公會通知有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/bkncn-20180428000302404-0428_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180428%2Fbkncn-20180428000302404-0428_05011_001.html&d=xzxPzewbXfXB2S0keWFP9NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=90feaa05\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180428/bkncn-20180428000302404-0428_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d1d34d7037eacc36223bf7bf191f54f1ab8fda9c","tid":646080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e683d9f2bd26706fc1e6c58735a466ae205687e","tid":646080,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c984ab12d93381091e23031a1795de7f0c61d316","tid":646080,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e683d9f2bd26706fc1e6c58735a466ae205687e","tid":646080,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif